      <title>台湾突然改变报道中国军事活动的方式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/taiwan-abruptly-changes-how-it-reports-china-military-activities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾在选出一位亲美总统几天后改变了报道中国在台湾地区军事活动的方式，北京称这位总统为“战争煽动者”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/taiwan-abruptly-changes-how-it-reports-china-military-activities</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 02:50:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国避免停工的支出法案扫清了参议院的第一个障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/us-spending-bill-to-avert-shutdown-clears-first-senate-hurdle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项旨在防止美国政府周六部分关闭的临时支出法案周二在参议院通过了首次程序测试，这表明该法案有望在最后期限前及时获得批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/us-spending-bill-to-avert-shutdown-clears-first-senate-hurdle</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 02:13:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国新冠死亡人数和低出生人数创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/china-population-extends-historic-decline-as-covid-deaths-surged</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2023年，中国人口延续了历史性下降趋势，北京结束严格的疫情限制措施后，死亡人数上升，出生率持续下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/china-population-extends-historic-decline-as-covid-deaths-surged</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 02:09:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称爱荷华州党团会议胜利导致中国市场“崩溃”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/trump-says-china-markets-crashed-on-iowa-caucus-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他在爱荷华州的大胜引发了中国股市的动荡，这表明北京方面担心他重新入主白宫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/trump-says-china-markets-crashed-on-iowa-caucus-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 02:02:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与拉马斯瓦米一起敦促新罕布什尔州拒绝黑利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/trump-joined-by-ramaswamy-urges-new-hampshire-to-reject-haley</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普刚刚在爱荷华州预选赛中取得创纪录的胜利，他敦促新罕布什尔州共和党人拒绝尼基·黑利，称她的候选资格得到了民主党的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/trump-joined-by-ramaswamy-urges-new-hampshire-to-reject-haley</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 01:39:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦谴责伊朗在其领土内发动致命袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/pakistan-condemns-iran-over-deadly-strike-inside-its-territory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦谴责其邻国伊朗涉嫌侵犯其领空，并在巴基斯坦领土内发动袭击，并称此次袭击造成两名儿童死亡，而该地区的紧张局势已经十分紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/pakistan-condemns-iran-over-deadly-strike-inside-its-territory</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 01:14:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着军火流动加剧，俄罗斯普京会见朝鲜最高特使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/russia-s-putin-meets-north-korea-s-top-envoy-as-arms-flow-builds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[弗拉基米尔·普京总统会见了来访的朝鲜外交部长，进行会谈，这可能会促进俄罗斯领导人前往平壤的行程，以及援助莫斯科对乌克兰战争的武器转让。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/russia-s-putin-meets-north-korea-s-top-envoy-as-arms-flow-builds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 00:52:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟和中国在达沃斯会议上提出电动汽车和白酒调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/eu-china-raise-ev-and-liquor-probes-during-a-meeting-in-davos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟委员会主席乌苏拉·冯德莱恩和中国国务院总理李强周二在达沃斯举行的一次会议上提出了各自对电动汽车和酒类的调查，强调了对新调查可能引发更广泛贸易冲突的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/eu-china-raise-ev-and-liquor-probes-during-a-meeting-in-davos</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 17:33:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员梅嫩德斯和他的妻子寻求对贿赂指控进行单独审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/senator-menendez-wife-seek-separate-trials-on-bribery-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议员鲍勃·梅南德斯 (Bob Menendez) 和他的妻子因贿赂指控而被一起起诉，他们各自要求法官进行单独审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/senator-menendez-wife-seek-separate-trials-on-bribery-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 13:42:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚考虑对高风险人工智能的使用进行强制性限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/australia-considering-mandatory-restrictions-on-high-risk-ai-use</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚将考虑对人工智能的发展引入强制性“护栏”，因为政府试图平衡新技术的生产力效益与包括传播虚假信息在内的潜在影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/australia-considering-mandatory-restrictions-on-high-risk-ai-use</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 13:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
